üîπ Popular Live Coins Stored in Wallets
Bitcoin (BTC) ‚Äì Long-term store of value, mostly kept in cold wallets
Ethereum (ETH) ‚Äì Used for smart contracts, DeFi, NFTs, commonly in hot wallets
USDT / USDC (Stablecoins) ‚Äì Used for trading and transfers, mostly hot wallets
