üîπ Wallet Usage in Real Time
Traders ‚Üí Hot wallets + exchange wallets
Investors (HODLers) ‚Üí Cold wallets for BTC & ETH
NFT Users ‚Üí Hot wallets like MetaMask
Institutions & Funds ‚Üí Hardware cold wallets

üîπ Current Trend (2025‚Äì2026)
Increased use of hardware wallets due to hacks
Growth of self-custody wallets over exchanges
Hot wallets integrated with DeFi, Web3, Metaverse apps
Cold wallets preferred after major exchange failures

  One-Line Summary
Hot wallets support fast access and real-time blockchain activity, while cold wallets ensure maximum protection for valuable cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum.

 

